dBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T06:24:58.000Z","msg":"我估樓主係曲線諷刺緊班連衛兵既<br />\n<br />\n佢地成日高舉香港有言論自由過支那，但係就一定要人表態支持自己既諗法，其實同支那人無分別，而且亦都唔洗立廿三條"},{"pid":"7b5e2b4323e2262f91533ba6c56feb95bd0049ed","tid":1186473,"uid":1751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T07:15:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9722506c0a3b30fab2646f93cbb3079c72b88bf5","tid":1186473,"uid":134012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T07:22:12.000Z","msg":"摘名<br />\n香港建國後一定要清算"}]}